          Direct farmer-to-buyer trade ensures farmers get fair value and buyers pay less without intermediaries.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow border hover:bg-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Better Prices</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          Competitive pricing helps farmers earn more, while buyers enjoy cost-effective purchases.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow border hover:bg-gray-100 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
        <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Trusted Network</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
